snippet.title: CyberVerse Showdown Trailer
snippet.description:
Welcome to CyberVerse Showdown, the ultimate card game set in a futuristic cyberpunk world! Unleash your strategic powers as you assemble a team of powerful cybernetic warriors, hackers, and technologically advanced humans to battle against AI rivals or P2P/LAN with a Friend.

Buy Now
https://store.steampowered.com/app/2708200/CyberVerse_Showdown
